name: Ninja Hanzo!
description:
Have you ever seen sparkling things in the sky at night? Do they change in brightness and sometimes seem to move? It could be the work of Ninja Hanzo.

Ninja Hanzo! is made for AR Art Book "Prosthetic Reality V.2" by EyeJack.
This artwork is a non AR video for hic et nunc version and also 1/3 of Ninja series.

Music Provider : mizuto
